{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"112763-bihonis","title":"ቢሆንስ?","description":"ሽያም እንቅልፍ ሲጫጫነው ጥርሱን ለመቦረሽ ይቸጋገራል፡፡ ይሁን እንጂ ትልልቅ ሕልሞችን ማለም ፈጽሞ አያስቸግረውም፡፡","language":"Amharic","langCode":"am","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Mezemir Girma"],"illustrators":["Hari Kumar Nair"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Ras Abebe Aregay Library","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/112763-bihonis"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/723050/size3/9093d145b12c1371d8ae9d976bfeb4ca.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/723050/size6/9093d145b12c1371d8ae9d976bfeb4ca.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10854/size6/95080dea5774836f4728dc9cca3df877.jpg","text":"ስሜ ሽያም\nነው፡፡ አስር ዓመቴ ነው፡፡\nትንሽ ቀጠን\nብልም ደፋር ነኝ!\nወደ ትምህርት\nቤት ለመሄድ ከእንቅልፍ መነሳት አስደሳች ነገር አይደለም፡፡\nጠዋት ስነሳ\nእንቅልፍ በጣም ይጫጫነኛል፡፡ የምወድቅ ሁሉ ይመስለኛል፡፡","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10855/size6/150bbd6785d122ffcee4709bb5fbb7b6.jpg","text":"ጥርሴን\nመቦረሽ ስጀምር ዓይኖቼ መከደን ይጀምራሉ፡፡\nእማ በጥድፊያ\nዳቦ ስትጋግር እሰማታለሁ፡፡\nአእምሮዬ\nበዝግታ ይንከራተታል፡፡\nብዙ ብዙ\nሃሳቦችም ይመጡልኛል፡፡","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10856/size6/29fee7997b93f57cd7c787d4e5e80af5.jpg","text":"አንገቴ\nከአሁኑ አስር እጥፍ ረጅም ቢሆንስ ኖሮ?\nግማሽ ትምህርት\nቤት፣ ግማሽ እቤት፣ የት እሆን ነበር?","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10857/size6/8ef925eac98a244e67858ac7093f532c.jpg","text":"እግሮቼ\nእንደ ዛፍ ረጅም ቢሆኑስ ኖሮ?\nየትምህርት\nቤቴ ሕንጻ ጉልበቴ ድረስ ይሆን ነበር!","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10858/size6/2cdf90f6209521efb78a278273c6835e.jpg","text":"እጆቼ\nጠንካራ ቢሆኑስ ኖሮ?\nእማማን\nማንሳት አይከብደኝም ነበር!","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10859/size6/76c96d2da7a6eda608fe0bacb9f38b04.jpg","text":"ለጥርሴ\nየሚጠጥርበት ምንም ነበር ባይኖርስ?\nመብላት\nየምችላቸውን ነገሮች እስኪ አስቧቸው!","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10860/size6/8f2d2e35555a921b51be255b208d8d3a.jpg","text":"ሆዴ\nእስከመጨረሻው ክብ ቢሆንስ?\nጓደኞቼ\nዘለው ከኔ ላይ ይነጥሩ ነበር!","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10861/size6/b8929d52a230715d68c37dd5ad250dc6.jpg","text":"ትልልቅና\nዝርግ ጆሮዎች ቢኖሩኝስ?\nከሩቅም\nከቅርብም ሁሉንም መስማት እችል ነበር!","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10862/size6/6da9e7456c9b34d2616e8202516b27ca.jpg","text":"እንዲህ\nቢሆንስ - ማለት እጀምራለሁ፡፡ ግን እማማ ትጮሃለች፡፡\n‹‹ሽያም፣\nይረፍድብሃል፡፡ ምን እያሰብክ ነው?››","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10863/size6/539b9866fb8cd510306f38754c292090.jpg","text":"ለካ\nአሁንም በእጄ ቡርሼን ይዤ ቆሜያለሁ፡፡\nከዚያም\nፈገግ ብዬ ስለትንሿ ምስጢራዊት መሬቴ አስባለሁ፡፡","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":10,"words":138}}